        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(whatsapp): convert GFM bold-italic without leaving literal asterisks",
        "body": "## Problem\n`markdownToWhatsApp` only strips one layer of `**`, so GFM `***bold-italic***` and `__*x*__` leave a literal `**` that WhatsApp renders as plain text. This is on the real outbound send / deliver-reply paths.\n\n## Fix\nHandle the combined strong+emphasis form before the plain bold rule so no stray `**` leaks through.\n\n## Proof\nAdded cases in `extensions/whatsapp/src/text-runtime.test.ts` — fail before the fix, pass after. Pure string transform, no live account.\n",
